handNote.seg:
Several groups of lines on the incipit page, alternating with black lines; 
two lines at the beginning of a new week (e.g. ; on , the rubrication has partly been extended to
the column b); 
metatextual elements pertaining to the categorization of antiphons
(antiphon-type designations, melodic-family designations, hallelujah numbers, incipits of antiphons lacking metatextual elements), in part or completely; 
occasionally, elements of numerals, punctuation signs, and marginal metatextual elements (bet designations).
